ugh primary digital channels. | LOW |\n| The Plant Man | Terminate | De minimis $235 plant/interior vendor; one-time office plant supply; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| The Riding House Cafe | Terminate | Small $265 London restaurant; one-time entertainment; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| The Virtual Legal Counsel Ltd | Terminate | Low $4.8K virtual legal counsel; consolidate legal work under primary law firms to avoid fragmented legal management. | Low; matters absorbed by primary legal counsel. | LOW |\n| Thomas Mansfield Solicitors Limited | Terminate | Small $1.1K employment law firm; minor one-time service; consolidate under primary employment counsel. | No material impact. | LOW |\n| Tiganda J.D.O.O. | Terminate | Small $432 Croatian vendor; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Till Trade D.O.O. | Terminate | De minimis $93 Croatian vendor; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Time Out Group | Terminate | Small $920 city guide/entertainment media; one-time sponsorship or ad placement; not a strategic vendor. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Tm Forum | Terminate | Small $510 TMForum membership; evaluate if active participation justifies cost; terminate if not leveraging membership benefits. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Tmforum | Terminate | Medium-spend $57.6K duplicate TMForum entity alongside TM Forum ($510); same organization with a significant billing discrepancy; investigate and terminate duplicate account — likely a billing error requiring urgent review. | MEDIUM: investigate whether this represents an active contract before terminating; possible billing or contract error. | MEDIUM |\n| T-Mobile | Consolidate | Low $3.4K T-Mobile mobile telecom; consolidate mobile device management and telecom under primary telecom provider agreement for unified billing and policy. | Low; mobile service continues under primary telecom. | LOW |\n| Tog Uk Properties Limited | Optimize | High-spend $26