lbox service; evaluate if required for registered address; if not, terminate; registered address maintainable through primary legal counsel. | Low; registered address manageable through primary legal provider. | LOW |\n| United Flow Ltd (The Goodness Project) | Terminate | Low $2.7K wellness/wellbeing program vendor; supplemental employee wellbeing; non-essential. | No critical dependency. | LOW |\n| Uptime Robot Service Provider Ltd | Consolidate | De minimis $78 uptime monitoring tool; consolidate with primary engineering monitoring stack (Datadog, AWS CloudWatch) to eliminate redundant point solutions. | No impact at this spend level. | LOW |\n| Urbani Eventi D.O.O. | Terminate | Small $851 Croatian events vendor; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Ustanova Za Medicinu Rada I Sporta Dr. Novacki | Consolidate | De minimis $20 third Croatian occupational medicine vendor; consolidate all three occupational health clinics under a single preferred provider for all Croatian employees. | No impact; same service from consolidated provider. | LOW |\n| Ustanova Za Zdravstvenu Skrb P.P. | Consolidate | Small $131 Croatian healthcare provider; consolidate Croatian employee health services under single preferred occupational health provider. | Low; healthcare services manageable through consolidated provider. | LOW |\n| Vector Capital Management Lp | Terminate | Low $32.4K investment/fund management fees; evaluate whether this is a managed fund fee or advisory service; if advisory, consolidate with primary finance advisors. | Low; advisory work absorbable by primary finance partner. | LOW |\n| Veniture D.O.O. | Terminate | Low $39.3K Croatian facilities/catering vendor; significant catering spend for Croatian offices; evaluate whether included in office management contract; renegotiate or terminate to capture material savings. | MEDIUM: if primary Croatian office catering provider, a replacement must be arranged for employees before exiting. | MEDIUM |\n| Visalogic Limited | Consolidate | Low $11.2K immigration/visa services; consolidate immigration services under primary HR/legal provider as part of a global mobility program to reduce fragmentation. | LOW: immigration cases transferable to primary immigration counsel with appropriate notice. | LOW |\n| Vistaprint | Terminate | De minimis $130 print/design service; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Vitality Works | Terminate | De minimis $182 employee wellness program; minor one-time; not a strategic vendor. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Vivat Fina Vina D.O.O. | Terminate | Small $467 Croatian wine vendor; one-time event/entertainment purchase; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Vodafone (Australian) | Consolidate | Low $3.7K Australian Vodafone mobile; consolidate Australian mobile services under primary telecom agreement for unified billing and policy. | Low; mobile service continues under primary telecom. | LOW |\n| Weking D.O.O. | Terminate | Medium-spend $144K Croatian facilities vendor; evaluate against Zagrebtower ($184K Optimize) to right-size total Croatian office footprint; if duplicating primary Croatian office management, terminate to eliminate overlap. | HIGH: if primary Croatian facilities management provider, immediate termination would disrupt office operations; transition plan required. | HIGH |\n| Westbrook Advisers | Terminate | Low $15.4K financial advisory firm; project-specific engagement; consolidate under primary financial advisors and terminate standalone relationship. | Low; advisory work absorbable by primary finance partner. | LOW |\n| Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd. | Terminate | Medium-spend $64K WeWork Singapore coworking space; evaluate Singapore headcount and workspace needs against cost; consolidate into primary office space or negotiate a flex workspace arrangement at lower cost. | HIGH: if primary Singapore workspace, employees need alternative arrangements before exit. | HIGH |\n| Winmaxi Tours & Travels | Terminate | Low $1K Indian travel agency; consolidate all travel through Navan TripActions travel management platform to enforce travel policy. | No impact; travel managed through Navan. | LOW |\n| Wolt Enterprises Oy | Terminate | De minimis $62 food delivery app; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Work Easy Space Solutions Private Limited | Terminate | Low $14.9K Indian coworking space; evaluate Indian headcount vs. workspace cost; consolidate into primary Indian office or terminate if headcount does not justify standalone space. | MEDIUM: if workspace for Indian employees, alternative must be secured before exit. | MEDIUM |\n| Workato, Inc. | Consolidate | Low $16.1K integration/automation platform (iPaaS) overlapping with Zapier ($167) and potentially native Salesforce integration; consolidate under primary integration platform to reduce point-to-point tool sprawl. | MEDIUM: active data integrations and workflows may depend on Workato; migration requires integration mapping. | MEDIUM |\n| Xenon Savjetovanje D.O.O. | Terminate | De minimis $164 Croatian consulting; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Yellow Submarine D.O.O. | Terminate | Small $486 Croatian vendor; one-time; not a vendor relationship. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Yoxel, Inc | Terminate | Low $2K US engineering tools vendor; minor one-time purchase; terminate. | No material impact. | LOW |\n| Zagrebacki Holding D.O.O. | Terminate | Small $143 Zagreb utility/holding company; likely statutory utility or administrative fee; reclassify as regulatory or include in office management contract. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Zagrebtower D.O.O. | Optimize | Medium-high spend $184K Zagreb office tower lease; primary Croatian headquarters facility; negotiate lease renewal terms, evaluate floor plate utilization, and explore sub-leasing of unused floors to reduce occupancy cost. | HIGH: primary Croatian office building; disruption would displace Zagreb-based workforce. | HIGH |\n| Zapier Inc. | Consolidate | De minimis $167 workflow automation; consolidate with Workato ($16K) under the primary integration platform to eliminate redundant automation tools. | No impact at this spend level. | LOW |\n| Zettanet | Consolidate | De minimis $183 network services; consolidate with primary network/connectivity vendor (Telefonica, Cloudcrossing) under unified network strategy. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Zivi Napitak D.O.O. | Terminate | Low $3.7K Croatian beverage vendor; likely office refreshments; evaluate whether covered by office management contract; otherwise terminate. | No impact. | LOW |\n| Zuric I Partneri Odvjetnicko Drustvo D.O.O. | Terminate | Low $24.1K Croatian law firm; consolidate Croatian legal work with primary international counsel; significant legal vendor fragmentation exists in Croatia that warrants rationalization. | LOW: Croatian legal matters transitionable to primary counsel with 30-day notice. | LOW |\n\n---\n\n## Summary Statistics\n\n| Metric | Count |\n|---|---|\n| Total vendors assessed | 386 |\n| Optimize | 22 |\n| Consolidate | 97 |\n| Terminate | 267 |\n| HIGH impact level | 28 |\n| MEDIUM impact level | 35 |\n| LOW impact level | 323 |\n\n---\n\n## Top 3 Cost Optimization Opportunities (Pre-Sized for STEP 09)\n\n| Rank | Vendor / Cluster | Combined Spend | Opportunity |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | Salesforce UK Ltd | $3,117,226 | License right-sizing + enterprise renegotiation; 10–20% reduction = $311K–$623K savings |\n| 2 | Navan (TripActions + Navan Inc combined) | $415,913 | Consolidate two entities + renegotiate unified contract; 15–25% reduction = $62K–$104K savings |\n| 3 | BDO LLP + RSM UK (audit/advisory consolidation) | $460,159 combined | Multi-year fee negotiation + scope rationalization; 10–15% reduction = $46K–$69K savings |\n\n---\n\nNow saving the updated Step 06 rationale memory."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":55007,