{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01TSsz6b5PJS46yj4BvZsUjq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The full **STEP 06 Vendor Decision Rationale Log** is complete — all 386 vendors documented with rationale, 30-day impact statement, and impact level.\n\n**Summary:**\n- **Optimize:** 22 vendors — strategic relationships needing renegotiation or right-sizing\n- **Consolidate:** 97 vendors — duplicate entities, overlapping tools, or fragmented category spend\n- **Terminate:** 267 vendors — long-tail, one-time, or negligible-spend vendors with no operational dependency\n\n**28 HIGH-impact vendors** flagged — these cannot be removed within 30 days without operational disruption. Core examples: Salesforce, AWS, Navan, TOG UK Properties, Cloudcrossing, BDO, Aetna, Jensten Insurance, Zagrebtower, Innovent Spaces, WeWork Singapore.\n\n**Top 3 pre-sized opportunities for STEP 09:**\n1. **Salesforce** ($3.1M) — license right-sizing + enterprise renegotiation: **$311K–$623K** potential savings\n2. **Navan consolidation** ($416K combined) — unify two entities + renegotiate: **$62K–$104K** potential savings\n3. **BDO + RSM audit/advisory** ($460K combined) — fee negotiation + scope rationalization: **$46K–$69K** potential savings"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":462,"cache_read_input_tokens":81325,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":462,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"30d5f0ff-1d06-4708-924e-f721060f0333","uuid":"90e0cb83-6700-46d4-bd42-8dd8da3376c8"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1280564,"duration_api_ms":1269235,"num_turns":5,"result":"The full **STEP 06 Vendor Decision Rationale Log** is complete — all 386 vendors documented with rationale, 30-day impact statement, and impact level.\n\n**Summary:**\n- **Optimize:** 22 vendors — strategic relationships needing renegotiation or right-sizing\n- **Consolidate:** 97 vendors — duplicate entities, overlapping tools, or fragmented category spend\n- **Terminate:** 267 vendors — long-tail, one-time, or negligible-spend vendors with no operational dependency\n\n**28 HIGH-impact vendors** flagged — these cannot be removed within 30 days without operational disruption. Core examples: Salesforce, AWS, Navan, TOG UK Properties, Cloudcrossing, BDO, Aetna, Jensten Insurance, Zagrebtower, Innovent Spaces, WeWork Singapore.\n\n**Top 3 pre-sized opportunities for STEP 09:**\n1. **Salesforce** ($3.1M) — license right-sizing + enterprise renegotiation: **$311K–$623K** potential savings\n2. **Navan consolidation** ($416K combined) — unify two entities + renegotiate: **$62K–$104K** potential savings\n3. **BDO + RSM audit/advisory** ($460K combined) — fee negotiation + scope rationalization: **$46K–$69K** potential savings","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"30d5f0ff-1d06-4708-924e-f721060f0333","total_cost_usd":1.7348637000000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":145402,"cache_read_input_tokens":203821,"output_tokens":51247,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":145402},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":25,"outputTokens":66490,"cacheReadInputTokens":317504,"cacheCreationInputTokens":171250,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.7348637000000002,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_s